          <p class="text-sm">
            Create your personal profile in just a few clicks â€” perfect for freelancers, coaches, and entrepreneurs.
          </p>
        </a>

        <a href="/en/smartpage" class="rounded-2xl p-5 text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-[#F5B400] to-[#E47E00]
